[h4 id=RuntSquad 
	" Runt Squad
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"These ghosts are surprisingly resilient. Thankfully their Max skill is a self destruct. I take advantage of this so I only need to kill one of them.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"+3 Frames
	$LF
