	"Without Fanelia this fight would be a nightmare. With it it's pretty manageable, I mostly just whittle her down with Rosiers while she's in her magic formation (weak to holy) and then finish with a No Mercy when she switches to attack form (weak to fire / ice / lightning.)
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"-2 Frames
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"I then lose 272 frames at the very end from Serene getting the Rosier level because of the change to Dark Death.
	$LF
