[h2 id=ClosingThoughts 
	"Closing Thoughts
	$LF
]h2
[div class=p 
	"This remake took quite a bit more time and effort than I originally intended but I'm happy I did it. The amount of improvement speaks for itself and I think I'm at a point where I can be very satisfied with the work I've done and the TAS I've created.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The overall slower pace might make it a bit of a niche offering but I'm optimistic that people will be entertained by the tricky routing, rng manipulation and the game's charm.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Big shoutouts to FractalFusion for suggesting a lot of the improvements that were implemented in this version.
	$LF
